# Import aliases

Always use `@/` aliases for imports from `src/`.

- Prefer: `import { X } from '@/lib/supabase'`, `import { Button } from '@/components/ui/button'`
- Avoid: `import { X } from '../lib/supabase'`, `import { Button } from '../../components/ui/button'`

Aliases configured: `@/*` → `src/*`, `@components/*` → `src/components/*`.
